---
title: Spaghetti All'Amatriciana with Salad
description: Spaghetti and meatballs are wonderful of course, but once you try Spaghetti All'Amatriciana, there may be no going back! This classic Lazio pasta dish capitalizes on the pure flavour of prosciutto and tomato! We recommend it with chili flakes, but promise it's just as delicious without.
